  "prompt": "What is the meaning of sending nudge in hike messenger?",
  "response": "In Hike Messenger, sending a nudge is a feature that allows you to get the attention of the person you are chatting with. When you send a nudge, the recipient's phone will vibrate, and they will receive a notification, even if they have muted the conversation or their phone is on silent. It's a way to prompt the other person to respond or to let them know that you are waiting for a reply. Nudges can be used in both one-on-one chats and group conversations.",
